fields.text:
# Health History Summary

**Patient:** {{ patient.full_name|default:"Unknown Patient" }}
**Date:** {{ submission.created_at|date:"F j, Y"|default:"Date not available" }}

---

## Clinical Overview

{% ai "Clinical Overview" %}
Based on the health history information provided, create a brief clinical overview (2-3 sentences) that:
- Summarizes the patient's overall health status
- Highlights any significant risk factors for anesthesia or surgery
- Notes any priority concerns requiring attention

Patient Information:
- Lifestyle: {% if submission.data.smoker %}Smoker{% endif %} {% if submission.data.drinks_alcohol %}Alcohol use{% endif %}
- Cardiac: {% if submission.data.high_blood_pressure %}HTN{% endif %} {% if submission.data.heart_disease %}Heart disease{% endif %}
- Respiratory: {% if submission.data.asthma_copd %}Asthma/COPD{% endif %} {% if submission.data.sleep_apnea %}Sleep apnea{% endif %}
- Other: {% if submission.data.diabetes %}Diabetes{% endif %} {% if submission.data.stroke %}CVA history{% endif %}
- Medications: {{ submission.data.medications|default:"None listed" }}
{% endai %}

---

{% if submission and submission.data %}

## Active Medical Conditions

### Cardiovascular
{% if submission.data.high_blood_pressure %}- High Blood Pressure
{% endif %}{% if submission.data.heart_disease %}- Heart Disease
{% endif %}{% if submission.data.blood_thinners %}- On Blood Thinners
{% endif %}{% if not submission.data.high_blood_pressure and not submission.data.heart_disease and not submission.data.blood_thinners %}None reported
{% endif %}

### Respiratory
{% if submission.data.asthma_copd %}- Asthma/COPD
{% endif %}{% if submission.data.sleep_apnea %}- Sleep Apnea
{% endif %}{% if not submission.data.asthma_copd and not submission.data.sleep_apnea %}None reported
{% endif %}

### Other Conditions
{% if submission.data.diabetes %}- Diabetes
{% endif %}{% if submission.data.kidney_problems %}- Kidney Problems
{% endif %}{% if submission.data.stroke %}- History of Stroke/TIA
{% endif %}{% if submission.data.seizures %}- Seizures/Epilepsy
{% endif %}{% if submission.data.bleeding_disorder %}- Bleeding/Clotting Disorder
{% endif %}{% if not submission.data.diabetes and not submission.data.kidney_problems and not submission.data.stroke and not submission.data.seizures and not submission.data.bleeding_disorder %}None reported
{% endif %}

---

## Lifestyle Factors

{% if submission.data.smoker %}- **Smoking:** Yes
{% else %}- **Smoking:** No
{% endif %}{% if submission.data.drinks_alcohol %}- **Alcohol:** Regular use
{% else %}- **Alcohol:** No regular use
{% endif %}

---

## Anesthesia History

{% if submission.data.anesthetic_problems %}
**Previous Anesthetic Issues:** Yes
{% if submission.data.anesthetic_problems_specify %}**Details:** {{ submission.data.anesthetic_problems_specify }}
{% endif %}
{% else %}
**Previous Anesthetic Issues:** None reported
{% endif %}

---

## Current Medications

{% if submission.data.medications %}
{{ submission.data.medications }}
{% else %}
No medications listed
{% endif %}

---

## Allergies

{% if submission.data.allergies and submission.data.allergies|length > 0 %}
{% for allergy in submission.data.allergies %}
- **{{ allergy.allergy_substance }}**: {{ allergy.allergy_reaction }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
No known allergies reported
{% endif %}

---

## Surgical History

{% if submission.data.surgeries and submission.data.surgeries|length > 0 %}
{% for surgery in submission.data.surgeries %}
- {{ surgery.surgery_procedure }}{% if surgery.surgery_date %} ({{ surgery.surgery_date }}){% endif %}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
No previous surgeries reported
{% endif %}

---

## Additional Information

{% if submission.data.other_conditions %}
{{ submission.data.other_conditions }}
{% else %}
None provided
{% endif %}

---

## Clinical Recommendations

{% ai "Recommendations" %}
Based on the patient's health history, provide 2-4 brief clinical recommendations regarding:
- Pre-operative workup needs (if any)
- Anesthetic considerations
- Monitoring requirements
- Any specialist consultations needed

Patient conditions:
{% if submission.data.high_blood_pressure %}- Hypertension
{% endif %}{% if submission.data.heart_disease %}- Heart disease
{% endif %}{% if submission.data.asthma_copd %}- Asthma/COPD
{% endif %}{% if submission.data.sleep_apnea %}- Sleep apnea
{% endif %}{% if submission.data.diabetes %}- Diabetes
{% endif %}{% if submission.data.blood_thinners %}- On anticoagulation
{% endif %}

Format as brief bullet points.
{% endai %}

{% else %}

**No submission data available.**

{% endif %}

---

